    "\n",
    "Our analysis begins with **Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)**. We will use data visualization techniques such as scatter plots and box plots to identify patterns or clusters of individuals who purchase homes earlier versus those who experience longer delays.\n",
    "\n",
    "In addition, we will perform **data cleaning** to address missing values and outliers that could distort the analysis and lead to unreliable results."
